<h2>The Legacy of the Realm</h2>
<p>
    In the age of steel and magic, <span class="gold"><%= stats.total_players %> brave souls</span> have set foot upon these dangerous lands. 
    Through hardship and triumph, they have collectively ascended <span class="gold"><%= stats.total_levels_gained %> levels</span> in their pursuit of power. 
    Yet, glory always exacts a price, because <span class="hp"><%= stats.total_deaths %> champions</span> have fallen in battle... lost, but not forgotten. 
    A few, overwhelmed by the weight of their journey, chose the coward's end, with <span class="muted"><%= stats.total_players_suicided %> weak souls</span> taking their own lives, 
    while <span class="hp"><%= stats.total_players_cheated %> heretics</span> were struck down by the gods for attempting to bypass the laws of the realm.
</p>

<h2>Echoes of the Battlefield</h2>
<p>
    The drums of war never truly fall silent because <span class="gold"><%= stats.total_battles %> battles</span> have been fought against the encroaching darkness, 
    resulting in the defeat of <span class="gold"><%= stats.total_enemies_killed %> formidable foes</span>. 
    From these conflicts, the survivors extracted vast wisdom, gaining a total of <span class="xp"><%= stats.total_xp_gained %> XP</span>. 
    But the wild is treacherous, as the hunters became the hunted and <span class="hp"><%= stats.total_ambushes %> ambushes</span> have occurred, nearly claiming those who walked unprepared.
</p>

<h2>The Toll of Survival</h2>
<p>
    Hardship is measured in blood and resilience. Our champions have shed <span class="hp"><%= stats.total_hp_lost %> HP</span>, 
    flesh torn by tooth and claw. Yet, the craft of the blacksmith has proven its worth, as armor deflected <span class="muted"><%= stats.total_damage_blocked %> damage</span>. 
    To mend their broken bodies, they have sought the warmth of the Inn and the delicious food inside, healing for a combined total of <span class="heal"><%= stats.total_hp_healed %> HP</span>.
</p>

<h2>The Flow of Fortune</h2>
<p>
    Wealth flows like a river through the pockets of the daring. A massive sum of <span class="gold">🪙 <%= stats.total_adena_generated %> Adena</span> has been pulled from the corpses of monsters and the hidden corners of the world. 
    Most of this fortune, however, returns to the realm's economy since <span class="gold">🪙 <%= stats.total_adena_spent %> Adena</span> has been spent on provisions and equipment. 
    The shops have flourished, selling <span class="gold"><%= stats.total_weapons_bought %> weapons</span> and <span class="gold"><%= stats.total_armors_bought %> armors</span> to those who would be king, 
    while the local Inn has served <span class="gold"><%= stats.total_food_bought %> meals</span> to keep the fires of life burning. 
    Today, the total wealth held within the pouches of all active wanderers stands at <span class="gold">🪙 <%= stats.total_adena %> Adena</span>.
</p>

